location.fullValue: Plan 1380 Plan, Entrada Del Pueblo at Rancho Sahuarita

data.description:
Range Priced-Seller will accept/or counter offers b/w $319,000 & $335,000. Come see this lovely 3Bed/2Bath home with a Den that has a Sparkling Pool!! A daytime visit is a necessity so you can feel the warm sun as it pours into the Great Room & highlights the easy living right off the Kitchen where guests can mingle with the cook. Spacious Bedrooms and a large Den, which can easily be converted to 4th bedroom, give privacy & space for everyone. Primary Bedroom Ensuite has dual vanities, a walk-in shower & separate soaking tub. The backyard won't disappoint either! Enjoy a dip in the Pool or sip a cold drink while you host family and friends for the big game under the covered patio. All this plus Rancho Sahuarita amenities & close to shopping & easy access to the interstate. Visit today! Community Amenities Include (from https://myranchosahuarita.com/community-amenities/):
Club Rancho Sahuarita
Located in the heart of the community is Club Rancho Sahuarita, which features a full fitness facility, meeting rooms, the Anza Sports Bar, our Kids Club children's facilities, athletic courts, a playground and Adventure Park, a full lap pool, and a Splash Park complete with water slides.

Parks and Trails
Rancho Sahuarita residents frequently rank our park and trail system as one of their favorite parts of the community. Two large neighborhood parks, 9 pocket parks, green spaces throughout the neighborhoods and 17 miles of walking and cycling trails. Trail system connects most of our parks and neighborhoods through a series of paths. These include the Safari Trail, the Wilderness Trail, and Anza Trail and others.

Neighborhood Parks and Pools
Rancho Sahuarita has two mini-recreation centers, located at the Parque Del Rio and the Parque Del Presidio. These centers are complete with pools, spas, basketball and sand volleyball courts, picnic areas, open space and playgrounds. 
Various events are also held here, like outdoor fitness classes and special events. For more information, please visit the Event Calendar on ActiveNet or check out what's new on the Rancho Sahuarita app!

Other Neighborhood Amenities:
The Armed Forces Tribute, which opened on July 4, 2016 with a private dedication ceremony, is dedicated to each branch of the Armed Forces: the Army, the Navy, the Air Force, the Marines and the Coast Guard. The new tribute and will present our community the chance to honor the veterans and active duty service members amongst us. Many other communities around the country have various types of physical tributes to honor the Armed Forces, and this is Rancho Sahuarita's opportunity to do the same tribute.

At the Parque Del Rio amenity, resident families can also enjoy the Flamingo Splash Pad.

This splash pad is is the shape of a semi-circle, and is made up of three colors. The centerpiece of the splash park is the addition of two 12-ft tall pink flamingos, and a series of special jets built into the pad which spray water upwards out of the deck.
